---
// src/components/index/HowItWorks.astro
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-3 font-semibold">Getting Started</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-4">Three Simple Steps</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed">From first conversation to live parish website — we handle everything.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-serif font-bold mx-auto mb-6">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-3">We Talk</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Tell us about your parish, your needs, and your vision. We'll guide you through everything.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-serif font-bold mx-auto mb-6">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-3">We Build</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">We design, build, and set up your complete parish website with all your content ready to go.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-serif font-bold mx-auto mb-6">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-3">You're Live</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Your parish goes online. We train your team and provide ongoing support and management forever.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
